Package: SamplePrevRatioMultiENG
Title: Sample Size Calculation for Prevalence Ratio Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Victor J.", "Vera-Ponce", email = "victor_jvp@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools to calculate sample size in studies
    using prevalence ratio as a measure of association, considering multivariable
    analysis and logistical aspects of the study. Includes functions for:
    * Sample size calculation considering covariables in the model
    * Statistical power evaluation
    * Study logistics planning
